###############################################################################
# Developer Guide (seeeye)
# 
# @version 0.1
###############################################################################

################################################## I. Pre-requisites ##########

1. Eclipse
	a. Download latest JEE version of eclipse
	b. Open eclipse and install latest version of M2Eclipse(http://download.eclipse.org/technology/m2e/releases), EGit plugins(http://download.eclipse.org/egit/updates)
	c. Change default encoding of *.properties/*.js files to UTF-8 in eclipse (Preferences->General->Content Types)
2. Install latest version of Tomcat and copy /documents/jstl-*.jar to ${tomcat}/lib
3. Install latest version of MySQL
4. Install msysgit or cygwin as git client

#################################################### II. Source Code ##########

1. Pull source code from git://github.com/emac/seeeye.git

############################################# III. Start Development ##########

1. Open eclipse and add the local git repository
2. Import all projects (under /product) from repository
3. Create a tomcat server in Servers view
4. Run "mvn clean package" against eyedpt.allinone project
5. DND eyedpt.web onto tomcat server and start server

Visit http://localhost:8080/seeeye
